<h2 id="ID-d280290c-3462-4552-b0ee-bceb21662511">Doom Emacs</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org6974d2e">
<p>
<a href="https://github.com/hlissner/doom-emacs">Home Page</a>.
Doom emacs is a <a href="20220428224740-emacs.html#ID-95b6342a-ca5b-4f59-9f08-6cbd3aedf7a2">emacs</a> configuration framework that is fast yet stays out of the way.
</p>

<p>
doom emacs has a a notable exception from the other configuration frameworks that it uses evil-mode out of the box.
</p>
